trans-unit.source: Represents the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) <see langword="all" /> element (compositor).
trans-unit.target: Representa o elemento <see langword="all" /> W3C (World Wide Web Consortium) (compositor).

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAll> class permits the elements in the group to appear (or not appear) in any order in the containing element.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAll> classe permite que os elementos no grupo a ser exibida (ou não aparecer) em qualquer ordem no elemento que contém.
